FIRST Baptist Church, 12, Oremerin Street, Ehin-Iga, Itire, Lagos, will hold its first revival in 2020, from Sunday. The church pastor, Rev. Dr. Stephen Afolabi, said the fourday revival, which is a stewardship revival, will end on March 11. He said the revivalist is Rev. Dr. Paul Opoola of First Baptist Church, Oshodi, Lagos, adding: “Attendees will receive salvation, deliverance from the bondage of sin and healing. Jesus Christ, the miracle worker, will perform signs and wonders in our midst. I’m expecting members and nonmembers to come and experience the Lord’s goodness.” 